          "Set $\\frac{\\sum f_i x_i}{\\sum f_i} = 6$ and solve for $p$."
        ],
        "derivation": "6 + 8 + 18 + 10 + 2p + 10 = 6(3+2+3+1+2) \\Rightarrow 52 + 2p = 6(11) \\Rightarrow 2p = 66 - 52 = 14 \\Rightarrow p = 7 \\text{ (Correction: Calculation check } 52+2p=66 \\Rightarrow 2p=14 \\Rightarrow p=7)"
