      "question": "The median of a distribution is 15 and the mean is 12. Find the mode using the empirical relationship.",
      "answer": "$Mode = 21$",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Use the empirical formula: $Mode = 3(Median) - 2(Mean)$.",
